---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';

/**
 * Medical-disclaimer draft (§6, Phase C7) — the sitewide expansion of
 * DisclaimerBlock's vetted wording. NOTE: the standard boilerplate
 * vocabulary of this genre is banned by the claims linter by design;
 * this draft uses the safe lexicon and counsel reviews the final text.
 */
---

<LegalLayout
  heading="Medical Disclaimer"
  title="Medical Disclaimer | Needle Girlie"
  description="Medical disclaimer for needlegirlie.com. Draft pending counsel review."
>
  <p>
    The content of this website — every page, description, and answer —
    is general information and education. It is not medical advice, and
    it does not replace an in-person evaluation by a licensed clinician.
  </p>

  <h2>No provider–patient relationship</h2>
  <p>
    Reading this website, or contacting the practice through it, does not
    create a provider–patient relationship with Amy Palacios, FNP. That
    relationship begins with a consultation and an individual evaluation.
  </p>

  <h2>Individual decisions, individual experiences</h2>
  <p>
    Whether any treatment fits your needs is decided together with Amy
    Palacios, FNP, during a consultation — never by a website. Individual
    experiences vary, and no outcome is promised or implied anywhere on
    this website.
  </p>

  <h2>Prescription medications</h2>
  <p>
    Some services described on this website involve prescription
    medications. They are offered only under clinician supervision,
    following an individual evaluation.
  </p>

  <h2>Emergencies</h2>
  <p>
    This website is not for emergencies. If you are experiencing a
    medical emergency, call 911 or go to the nearest emergency room.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
